
amateur
=============


n.[C]可數名詞
-------------

1. (科學, 藝術, 運動等的)業餘從事者
Our actors were all enthusiastic amateurs. 我們的演員都是熱心的業餘愛好者。

2. 外行; 粗通(某一行)的人
The young politician is an `amateur` at manipulating public opinion. 那個年輕政客在操縱輿論方面是個外行。

3. 愛好者[(+of)]

a.[Z]形容詞
-------------

1. 業餘的
The pictures were taken by an `amateur` photographer. 
這些照片是一位業餘攝影師拍的。

2. 外行的, 不熟練的
Her acting was very amateur. 她的演技很難恭維。





1. able to read the word
2. https://www.google.com.tw/#q=contradictory&safe=off&tbs=dfn:1
